cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.CV, cs.DS 

This paper is about automated quality management for machine learning (ML) application development, specifically focusing on detecting and measuring overfitting. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SE (Software Engineering) as they are also relevant to the topic. Additionally, since the paper mentions image classification as an example application, cs.CV (Computer Vision) is a possible sub-category. Finally, since the paper discusses techniques for optimizing data sizes, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also a possible sub-category.
